  "description": "A wide shot captures a bustling port scene at either dawn or dusk. Several massive container ships are docked alongside a pier, loaded with colorful shipping containers stacked high.  Large, white gantry cranes loom over the ships, actively handling cargo. The water in the foreground reflects the lights and colors of the scene, creating shimmering, vertical streaks. The sky is a soft blend of blues and oranges, suggesting the transition between day and night.  The overall impression is one of industrial activity and global trade.",
